
## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Camera**: Uniview TIC7626EL thermal camera (RTSP streaming)
- **Backend**: Python 3.9+
  - OpenCV (video processing)
  - YOLOv8 (object detection)
  - FastAPI (REST API)
  - PostgreSQL (detection logging)
- **Frontend**: Antigravity IDE (visual dashboard)
- **Deployment**: Docker

